OL,3,C22-year-old man arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof murder after man dies in Welshpool
OL,6,FA 22-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder and remains in
OL,8,Fpolice custody after the death of a
OL,9,Fman in Welshpool.
OL,11,FDyfed-Powys Police were called to
OL,12,FChurch Street at approximately 1am on
OL,13,FSunday (June 28) after reports a man
OL,14,Fhad been injured, where he shortly
OL,15,Fdied at the scene.
OL,17,FPolice presence is expected in the
OL,18,Farea over the coming days while
OL,19,Finvestigations continue.
